OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fsunny evening will lead to a largely
OL,7,Fclear night. Patchy mist and cloud
OL,8,Fhowever will move over the Pennines
OL,9,Flater. A warm night, especially in
OL,10,Furban areas. Moderate easterly winds,
OL,11,Fwith some gustiness over high ground.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day
OL,14,Fonce any early morning low cloud and
OL,15,Fmist clears. Feeling very warm,
OL,16,Fespecially in the strong sunshine.
OL,17,FEasterly winds persisting although
OL,18,Feasing slightly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
